data.description: This well maintained 4 Br 2.5 bath home is ready new owners to enjoy! The style of this home allows for most of your daily living to be on one level. The main level features a large sunny living room that is open to the dining room, which is also open to the kitchen. This level includes 3 spacious bedrooms. The main bedroom has a full bath attached. There is also a full hall bathroom on this level. The lower level is full daylight too and includes another bedroom, 1/2 bath, and a very large family room/game room. This large room has a fire place and sliding doors out to a wide patio. This level is great for relaxing or entertaining. This home includes a 1 car garage that has inside access; a level, open, fenced yard; and an above ground pool adjacent to the back patio.  The drive way was expanded to give extra space for parking.  All this in a neighborhood location with sidewalks and easy commuting routes!
